      513.58,
      535.73,
      586.63
    ],
    "text": "South-West monsoon is gradually getting established over the island. Showers or thundershowers will occur at times in Western, Sabaragamuwa, Central and North-western provinces and in Galle and Matara districts.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
